.SH Description
.SP 5 5

Thie method returns the values of the race which determine visibility.
It returns an array of the format:
.EP
.SP 5 5
({
.EP
.SP 5 5
   dark
.EP
.SP 5 5
   pitch dark,
.EP
.SP 5 5
   bright light,
.EP
.SP 5 5
   bright
.EP
.SP 5 5
})
.EP

